{"body": "Persons subject to immigration control are a class of person prescribed for the purposes of paragraph 2(9)(b) of Schedule 1A to the 1992 Act and which must not be included in an authority\u2019s scheme.\n. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .\n\u201cPerson subject to immigration control\u201d has the same meaning as in section 115(9) of the Immigration and Asylum Act 1999.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2012/2885 reg. 13", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885/13", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-06-07-uk-council-tax-reduction", "heading": "Regulation 13", "id": "7771a742-9129-59aa-9ef1-3012fbd088a3", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "2885", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "13", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2012"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2012/2885 reg. 13", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W"], "references_to": ["uksi/2012/2885", "ukia/2012/413"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 13, "parent_citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2012/2885", "parent_id": "f9da00e5-490c-508d-9da0-4bb9b7f5d388", "source_as_of": "2026-06-07-uk-council-tax-reduction", "source_document_id": "uksi/2012/2885", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/regulation/13", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-06-07-uk-council-tax-reduction/uksi/2012/2885/regulation-13.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2012/2885/regulation/13", "version": "2026-06-07-uk-council-tax-reduction"}
